{"tid":889311,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"曾幾何時 唉 已經成為咗我嘅口頭禪","createTime":"2018-11-04T13:04:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T19:12:53.000Z","uid":150662,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"aa79f6ca387ac99591c5f9e3c7ce9ac74b2f4315","tid":889311,"uid":150662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T13:04:37.000Z","msg":"無論讀書定返PT  開始令到我煩多咗 多咗野諗 唔似得好似中學咁鳩下鳩下又一日  <br />\n<br />\n有時要煩學業  有時要煩工作  有時要煩家庭  <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一日唉咗幾廿次都唔知  直至到同學 屋企人屌鳩你唉完未先知啱啱自己又不自覺咁唉咗一聲<br />\n<br />\n有時係度諗 唉咁多聲或多或少係對自己同埋呢個社會嘅一種無力感  <br />\n<br />\n呢個時候我會問一問自己係咪唔夠努力 唔夠上進  一諗到呢啲野又唉咗一聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唉我真係好想自己一個人出去旅行  散下心  離開一個令到我日唉夜唉嘅地方唞啖氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f63056885479985a318204cb89e5d82049c64b3a","tid":889311,"uid":150662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T13:06:15.000Z","msg":"其實自己係咪庸人自擾緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54d6736a2b2db612d85bb842a888ed7b3a24ef33","tid":889311,"uid":1706,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T13:07:16.000Z","msg":"同你一樣，而家除左唉之外唔知仲有咩助語詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比人問我做咩成日唉先發覺我有咁既習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34b670fb283e88cf16e15a867a13ff3e5c968b5c","tid":889311,"uid":1706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f63056885479985a318204cb89e5d82049c64b3a","tid":889311,"uid":150662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T13:06:15.000Z","msg":"其實自己係咪庸人自擾緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T13:09:01.000Z","msg":"講唔上有咩實際原因，淨係覺得個心好似有野壓住，唉出黎好似會緩和啲咁。。。"},{"pid":"399cdb3997d55da4db1e7c6eb94c5b991a34fbab","tid":889311,"uid":150662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"